Template 6 - AI Use Case Registry
The registry should be treated as the operating center of the program. Every approved, pending, paused,
rejected, or retired use case should show up here with enough detail to support review and leadership
reporting.
Registry discipline: If the use case is not in the registry, governance is mostly just a PowerPoint hobby.
