Template 7 - Shadow AI Discovery Workflow and Log
Recommended workflow
 Identify suspected unapproved AI tools through user interviews, procurement signals, browser or SaaS
reviews, and manager disclosure.
 Confirm the business owner, purpose, and what data is being entered or connected.
 Determine whether the tool is already approved, conditionally acceptable, or prohibited.
 Assign a risk level and decide whether to allow, replace, restrict, or stop the usage.
 Track remediation owners, dates, and communication actions in the log below.
